io.libraft.agent.configuration
Class RaftDatabaseConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  io.libraft.agent.configuration.RaftDatabaseConfiguration

public final class RaftDatabaseConfiguration
extends Object

Represents the configuration for the database backend to be used as the persistent store for Log and Store. Contains the following properties:

  • driverClass
  • url
  • user
  • password
See the project README.md for more on the configuration.
